text: Did you know that your ribs move about 5 million times a year, every time you breathe? I haven't counted them, yet!!
Every cigarette smoked cuts at least five minutes of life on average, which is roughly the time it takes to smoke one cigarette.
Incredible: The human body contains over a billion miles of DNA.
An important reason to stop smoking: Smoking while pregnant increases the chances of spontaneous abortions stillbirths and premature labor.
Fact: A healthy eating plan is one that is low in saturated fats, trans fats, cholesterol, salt (sodium), and added sugars.
"Life is not living, but living in health." Martial, Roman poet
"We must turn to nature itself, to the observations of the body in health and in disease to learn the truth." Hippocrates
�May all nurture their children and grand children properly and be blessed with 100 years of healthy life.� Rig Veda
�Wondering's healthy. Broadens the mind. Opens you up to all sorts of stray thoughts and possibilities.� Charles de Lint
�Health is my expected heaven.� John Keats (English Romantic Poet. 1795-1821)
�Happiness is good health and a bad memory.� Ingrid Bergman
�Health is the state about which medicine has nothing to say.� W. H. Auden
The part can never be well unless the whole is well. by Plato
It ain't what you don't know that gets you into trouble. It's what you know for sure that just ain't so. - M. Twain
